												<h2>Careers</h2>
																														<div id="node-341" class="node">

		
		
	<div class="content" style="width: 450px; float: left;">
		<p>Electrosonic is a leading provider of audio-visual systems and service support with offices around the world. Our success is due in large part to the dedication and expertise of our employees.</p>
<p>Electrosonic places great emphasis on finding the right fit for each individual to flourish and build a career path. Career development for all is supported through job specific training initiatives that provide opportunities for career growth. This ensures that Electrosonic remains at the cutting edge of technology and maximizes the potential of each employee.</p>
<p>Benefits:</p>
<ul>
<li>Medical, Dental, Vision, and Life Insurance</li>
<li>Company Matched 401k Plan</li>
<li>Vacation and Sick Time Off</li>
<li>Generous Company Holiday Schedule</li>
</ul>
<p>If you’re looking for a career within a fast paced, innovative and stimulating environment, then please look at our current vacancies by following one of the links below:</p>
<p><a href="http://electrosonic.applicantpro.com/jobs/">USA career opportunities</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.electrosonic.co.uk/content/career-opportunities-uk-and-europe">UK and Europe career opportunities</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.electrosonic.com/solutionsasia/solution/career-opportunities-asia">Asia career opportunities</a></p>
	</div>
	
		
